{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_13","type":"agent_message","text":"The source confirms two backoff callers: execution already has `exc.kind`, while planning’s `ReasonerUnavailable` carries only a transient flag, so planning must pass `None`. One adjacent runtime-circuit threshold also uses the uniform budget; aligning that threshold is necessary for the required “attempt 3 requeues, no block” execution proof without altering block construction or resolution."}}
